content.rendered: Jual mesin absensi sidik jari ZKTECO tersedia dengan type fingerprint Akses Control ZKTECO F18 harga murah cuman Rp2,068,710!! Anda dapat memantau kegiatan / aktivitas sehari-hari dengan jarak jauh secara real time. fingerprint ZKTECO Akses Control ZKTECO F18 mempunyai spesifikasi, diantaranya: Screen: 2.4 inch TFT-LCD color screen Fingerprint Capacity: 3,000 Templates Card Capacity: 5,000 (Optional) ID / MIFARE / HID Event Capacity: 30,000 Sensor: ZK Optical Sensor Algorithm Version: ZK Finger V9.0 & 10.0 Communication: TCP / IP, RS232 / 485, USB-Host Access Control Interface: Electric Lock, Door Sensor, Exit Button, Alarm, Doorbell Wiegand: Input, Output and SRB Standard Functions: Daylight Saving Time, Registration Consultation, Anti-Passback, External Fingerprint Reader for RS485, Printer (Optional) Power supply: 12V DC, 3A Operating Temperature: 0 ° C to 45 ° C Operating Humidity: 20% up to 80% Dimensions: 80 x 183 x 42 mm
